# Cron Jobs

## Cos'è
Cron is a scheduler that allows tasks to run automatically at specified intervals.

## Perché è importante
Scheduling repetitive tasks improves efficiency and is essential for system maintenance and automation.

## Comandi principali
```bash
crontab -e            # Edit user cron jobs
crontab -l            # List cron jobs
* * * * * /path/to/script.sh  # Cron timing format

## Errori comuni
- Using incorrect timing format
- Forgetting to give execute permissions to scripts
- Not specifying full paths in cron jobs
